Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------op--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:07.43,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.25,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:22.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:29.87,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:37.58,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:43.71,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:48.52,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:52.51,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:59.52,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:03.12,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:07.34,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:13.94,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:17.71,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:21.61,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:30.67,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:07.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這份真情實感　好想將它傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.25,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了不沉溺於一去不返的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:22.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊緊擁抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:29.87,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷於那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:37.58,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方應該有什麼正等待著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:43.71,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝著那未完結的故事　飛奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:48.52,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷著一顆真誠的心向著那千難萬險之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:52.51,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}張開心靈的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:59.52,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循環傳遞著一個訊息　幸福就存於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:03.12,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下來的少許勇氣　儘管須以眼淚相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:07.34,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但這或許正是變強的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:13.94,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}溫暖的迭句　想要永遠將這份珍重守護
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:17.71,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心緒交織　感受著這其中的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:21.61,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以說沒有人是孤身隻影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:30.67,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片藍天下　好想將這份真情實感傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:20.62,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:29.41,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:38.75,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:47.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:50.10,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.19,0:22:58.72,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.91,0:23:07.60,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:16.78,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.03,0:23:27.98,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:20.62,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷揣著內心深處收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:29.41,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}躍入未知的前方　那裡有什麼正等待著我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:38.75,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是與未來共鳴　不斷憶起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:47.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就會生出勇氣　就能變得堅強　也就不再是獨自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:50.10,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（讓你傾聽）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.19,0:22:58.72,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定會與你相遇　我會帶著真誠的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.91,0:23:07.60,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接夢想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:16.78,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}與其坐擁這無限的時刻　倒不如追趕那絢爛的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.03,0:23:27.98,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　總有一天會讓你傾聽那夢中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然買得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希就知道不停地往筐裡放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…滑了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒傷著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…雞蛋碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  待會兒再買就是了  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下我賠錢給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真是好大的風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是第一陣春風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吹春香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:25.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（春香的讀音於春風相近）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這笑話真冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞蛋的錢你會出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:39.98,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第10碗  舍華求實的年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種笑話還真受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來就好笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子你平時都看什麼節目？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:03:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這丫頭只知道看新聞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？那麼死板怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且新聞有什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說社會上發生的各種事都很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社會上的…是指案件啊事故什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是活動或體育新聞之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去下洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  快完事回來說些豐富多彩的新聞聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們養貓了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  偶爾會跑來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是四樓  怎麼爬到陽台上的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是坐電梯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是在騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子上廁所好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？想這麼玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩？指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  要鑽進被爐裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘拿手帕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子是多麼…多麼的可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是淳子轉世嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家沒死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的蜜柑！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小氣幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…今天請各位光臨  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有重要的事情要宣佈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天會讓身邊的蠢貨們變得活躍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨們是指誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是夏奈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  當然是真希你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢  我們為了能迅速地吐蠢貨們的槽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須對此進行練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家的小千秋到底接受了怎樣的教育啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面跟著我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一億日元而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才一億日元而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是要吐在什麼地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞蝦米啊  你這蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞蝦米啊  你這蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰吐的槽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  真希  大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋她們開始練吐槽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？這不是好事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  真希你覺得沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們不帶你一起練習吐槽  就當你是白癡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:06:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  千秋用文件夾把蠢貨和正常人分得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有家人用的文件夾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有春香享有桌面上捷徑的待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼  千秋  電腦拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正忙著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些  夏奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才看了看春香買的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚飯應該是烤魚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉…我想吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是前些天不是剛吃過牛肉火鍋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉…我想吃烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  烤肉不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…烤好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～牛舌真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希  雞軟骨  雞軟骨也烤好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後還有…裡脊  裡脊也不能沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  賞花啊  不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:06:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賞花？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  是裡～脊～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花現在還是花苞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對啦  是裡脊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得像花苞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花苞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.01,0:07:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我跟你說  剛才千秋把裡脊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了  蠢貨！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  小心感冒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  千秋怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋說想去賞花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賞花？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.59,0:07:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是賞花  不如說是去看花苞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然天氣還很冷…要去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是期待啊  裡脊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  錯了  是賞花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得  也叫上冬木吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好啊  吃完飯我過去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別給人家添麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才不會去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冬木說他要去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了  那就按人數準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  洗澡水燒好了  你去洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣啊  去吧  我也去我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在賞花是不是早了點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是夏奈提議的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然像她的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在早了點怎麼都不勸勸她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聊什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要去賞花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花都還沒開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？那也能叫賞花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠傻的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待啊  烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？不是賞花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啥不好  邊賞花邊烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聊什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說大家一起去賞花的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賞花？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是早了點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  總之來賞花吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我已經有安排了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！比賞花還重要的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…要模擬考…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你就天天對著重要的模擬考睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  藤岡  你明天有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:09:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…明天的話  嗯  有空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那就來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  雖然不知道是要做什麼…我就打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位早！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都該知道  賞花的關鍵是占個好位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  採購就更不用說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  我想趁現在決定各自的分工
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  阿真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來是沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  可以的話我來占位置好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去占位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是採購比較有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去採購算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做什麼好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:52.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  三個男生去占位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？三個？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛幹嘛  別猶豫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:02.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那內田  你來負責採購了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:03.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:06.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說夏奈  可以買很多零食嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  多指教…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就等下在櫻花樹下見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待各位的戰果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈她們還真是夠精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣才討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣才舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香的家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人安心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼了  過來幫忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說光吃烤肉太單調的不是真希你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  我來幫忙就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  圍裙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  合適嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副扮相怎麼會合適嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  夏奈都這麼吩咐了也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你是最近才搬來這裡的吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  你跟千秋是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一堆無關的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當的便宜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  我這麼會買東西還真是麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會有需要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓罐頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你邊賞花邊吃貓罐頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  全部集齊的話可以拼成房子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一盒裡只有一個零件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆給我適可而止吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希你沒事吧  有沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  拿這個擦擦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是夏奈她們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了…哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要賞花嗎  也加我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有垃圾桶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…不過這種事情還是要問問女孩子的意見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？呃…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不錯吧…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那就選這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生在這方面的眼光還是差些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  問了個奇怪問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我看起來像男孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來  果汁還有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須快點去夏奈她們那兒…便當也還…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  沒關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下來嘗嘗這特製木天蓼果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學她們好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道帶TS過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼  TS是什麼的縮寫？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Tandem Screen{\r}\N上下屏幕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冬馬  藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這裡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有的事  不是第一批嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一天也不會有第二批人來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來看  全部集齊的話能拼個房子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～其它還買什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓糧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  春香姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  她還沒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該快來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:16:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道已經在那邊烤上肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  怎麼想也不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學她真有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏奈  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼晚啊  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來  過來一起喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來嘛…夏奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去那邊有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要商量一下接下來怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要走了  之後再喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:16:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  給你禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？你都做什麼去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香她…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去遲了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指望你也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  來  吉野拿著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是果汁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  都有什麼味道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故將有五危
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:18:02.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（出自孫子兵法「九變第八」）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:17:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必死可殺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必生可虜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忿速可侮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廉潔可辱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛民可煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:15.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射將先射馬！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不冷嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  差不多該去賞花…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是千秋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  為你的到來乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢…就蒸了一下…蒸的東西就這樣…就這樣噴出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊  真的好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  千秋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託  不管是誰趕緊回來個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下得好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  現在是世界上最長且最讓人難耐的三分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我用自己的零用錢買的  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡啊  突然就下起雨來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的  都成落湯雞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上天氣預報不是說過會下雨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒帶傘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊換衣服吧  我給你放洗澡水去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須死在這裡  不能讓你再活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  要殺就動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死你的前未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼你要背叛組織
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  再過十分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是暖身子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完這個就去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要  哪種
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你們兩個怎麼都在吃泡麵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就該吃晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香要吃嗎  很香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…那我也吃一點兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.54,0:23:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗鼻子時候有被嗆到的經歷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為鼻液和水的濃度不同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用生理鹽水洗的話就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.69,0:23:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著只要按住半邊鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用鼻子吸水  然後把流到嘴裡的水吐出來  就通暢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就是如何習慣了  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.92,0:23:46.09,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(250,0)}第11碗  「果然不妙了」
